Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
21/01/2025	navkc1 JIRA Bug MTN-33812: EUP - FR - Additional Storage Days - Date Selection

*/

vars

begin
	self.doChangeDate();
epilog

end;</source>
        <Parameter name="editMask" type="JadeEditMask" usage="input"/>
    </JadeMethod>
